card.text:
Flying, ward {2}
Play with two cards in your hand revealed.
When this attacks or dies, shuffle up to two cards from your hand into your library and draw that many cards.

Ward {U}
Draw from an opponent’s library instead of your own.
Whenever you play or cast a card you don’t own, create a treasure token.

When this enters, choose target creature.
Equipped creature is a copy of the chosen creature. (Exactly as the chosen creature was when this entered.)
Equip {2/U}

Companion — Your starting deck contains at least ten equipment cards.
Double strike, ward {1}
When this enters or when it attacks while equipped, put two charge counters on it. Then tutor an equipment with mana value less than or equal to the number of charge counters on it to the battlefield.
